"These endpoints allow runtime management of the lookup client and server."
" They are useful for dynamically reconfiguring the lookup mechanism "
"without restarting the service."
msgstr "这些端点允许对查找客户端和服务器进行运行时管理。它们对于在不重启服务的情况下动态重新配置查找机制非常有用。"

